35
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:38,400
We will see if I can take him or not eventually.

36
00:03:38,500 --> 00:03:43,400
Come on! Take this man away and lock him up!

37
00:03:56,640 --> 00:03:58,700
Aigoo.

38
