You're late.

49
00:05:14,750 --> 00:05:16,560
You're the one who came earlier.

50
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:19,740
You're bolder than I thought. You have the nerve to come here.

51
00:05:19,740 --> 00:05:22,200
That's what I should be saying.

52
00:05:22,200 --> 00:05:25,920
Make sure you grit your teeth.

53
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:30,360
You're confident with your fist when your handwriting is terrible?

54
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:34,030
How dare you point out my handwriting?

55
00:05:34,030 --> 00:05:36,020
Your hand is trembling.

56
00:05:36,020 --> 00:05:37,120
What?

57
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:39,860
Let's make this short.

58
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:56,300
That hurt.

59
00:06:11,400 --> 00:06:15,870
You have offended Silla's sacred Najeong, capture the criminals!

60
00:06:15,870 --> 00:06:17,630
Yes!

61
00:06:23,080 --> 00:06:25,600
Go!

62
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:27,720
- Let go.
- Let me go!!

63
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:30,280
Let go!

64
00:06:30,280 --> 00:06:32,160
Let go!

65
00:06:32,160 --> 00:06:33,860
Let go!

66
00:06:33,860 --> 00:06:36,570
Let go!

67
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:42,460
Tie them all up!

68
00:06:42,460 --> 00:06:45,280
Tie them!

69
00:06:47,860 --> 00:06:50,960
Who was arrested, where?

70
00:06:51,900 --> 00:06:56,490
What do you mean Najeong? They started a fight at Najeong?

71
00:06:58,490 --> 00:07:02,860
If Queen Dowager decides to kill them, we have nothing to say.

72
00:07:02,860 --> 00:07:06,290
What do you mean kill? How can you say that?

73
00:07:06,290 --> 00:07:08,160
Do you know where Najeong is?

74
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:13,030
It was where King Park Hyeokgeose (Founder of Silla) was born. It's a sacred place.

75
00:07:13,790 --> 00:07:17,720
I, Park Young Shil, am trying to become king

76
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:23,130
because Silla originally belonged to the Park family. But he dared to have a brawl there?

77
00:07:23,130 --> 00:07:25,960
He is none other than Park Yeong Sil's adopted son?

78
00:07:26,990 --> 00:07:30,550
Without Ban Ryu, the Park family will have no king.

79
00:07:30,550 --> 00:07:33,840
Did you forget why you came here?

80
00:07:34,950 --> 00:07:39,400
Are you really going to end everything here?

81
00:07:50,880 --> 00:07:52,690
It's all because of you!

82
00:07:53,380 --> 00:07:55,870
This poop guy is so annoying.

83
00:07:55,870 --> 00:07:58,620
D-Did you just call me poop?

84
00:07:58,620 --> 00:08:02,730
If you hadn't sent that message, then we wouldn't be in this mess!

85
00:08:02,730 --> 00:08:06,130
What do you mean that message? You're the one—

86
00:08:06,130 --> 00:08:08,790
What is the commotion over here?!

87
00:08:10,530 --> 00:08:15,560
Look here. I want to say something to my father. My father is—

88
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:17,300
You...

89
00:08:19,790 --> 00:08:23,400
are still clueless, right?

90
00:08:23,400 --> 00:08:26,430
If you enter here alive, you will leave here dead.

91
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:34,000
Even if you came here dead, you would leave as bones.

92
00:08:37,220 --> 00:08:39,630
Don't be ill-mannered and wait quietly.

93
00:08:39,630 --> 00:08:44,590
The queen dowager is in the middle of wondering what to do with you guys.

94
00:08:57,260 --> 00:09:00,100
Have they always left offenders

95
00:09:01,100 --> 00:09:04,400
to die without a sip of water?

96
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:07,540
Ah, such a naïve guy.

97
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:13,490
How are you sleepy and thirsty in the middle of all this?

98
00:09:14,300 --> 00:09:18,430
Let's stop this in this situation, please!

99
00:09:33,290 --> 00:09:38,430
Hey. Hey!

100
00:09:39,500 --> 00:09:43,550
I'll need to wake him up to know what happened to Father.

101
00:09:58,100 --> 00:10:01,460
He'll be okay. Your father.

102
00:10:01,460 --> 00:10:03,310
Where is he is right now?

103
00:10:03,310 --> 00:10:07,430
Did he not get hurt? Where is he right now?

104
00:10:11,830 --> 00:10:16,300
How can I believe you? We haven't heard from him yet.

105
00:10:16,300 --> 00:10:19,400
I heard you interrupted the ceremonial walk and made a scene.

106
00:10:23,620 --> 00:10:27,140
How can I believe that?

107
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:34,220
I...

108
00:10:35,570 --> 00:10:38,770
I won't allow anyone else to die in my place.

109
00:10:39,550 --> 00:10:41,680
So,

110
00:10:44,250 --> 00:10:46,150
don't cry.

111
00:11:19,610 --> 00:11:24,310
You must be thirsty and you must feel like your legs will fall off.

112
00:11:24,310 --> 00:11:30,330
But the bad news is we haven't even started the torture yet.

113
00:11:30,330 --> 00:11:34,410
As you are here for committing high treason at Sacred Najeong.

114
00:11:34,410 --> 00:11:36,990
You will be killed with a terrible punishment.

115
00:11:36,990 --> 00:11:40,620
This is the queen dowager's final command.

116
00:11:45,240 --> 00:11:47,640
Tie these people to the chairs!

117
00:11:47,640 --> 00:11:49,210
Yes!

118
00:11:58,530 --> 00:12:02,550
We have nothing to say from our mouths.

119
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:09,500
Please review our foolish children with your magnanimous tolerance.

120
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:16,200
No way. Is your son amongst those criminals?

121
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:22,500
I sincerely apologize. I have been an incompetent father.

122
00:12:22,500 --> 00:12:25,460
Please spare their lives.

123
00:12:27,350 --> 00:12:31,830
Even if the queen dowager kills our children, we can't say anything!

124
00:12:31,830 --> 00:12:36,430
I don't understand this. How can they do that in Najeong?

125
00:12:37,370 --> 00:12:39,700
How did the palace guards know?

126
00:12:39,700 --> 00:12:43,510
It was as if they were waiting there for it to happen, isn't it so?

127
00:12:48,470 --> 00:12:49,720
What is this?

128
00:12:49,720 --> 00:12:52,000
It's a message that Ban Ryu received.

129
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:55,420
Kim Seup's son, Soo Ho, received it too.

130
00:12:55,420 --> 00:12:58,840
- Then does this mean—
- Our children were caught in a trap.

131
00:12:58,840 --> 00:13:00,310
What is this?

132
00:13:02,530 --> 00:13:07,350
The queen dowager is determined to make Hwarang, this is why...

133
00:13:07,350 --> 00:13:12,230
This time, we lost.

134
00:13:13,050 --> 00:13:18,480
Let us make Hwarang just as the queen dowager expects.

135
00:13:18,480 --> 00:13:20,090
Gakgan. (Park Yeong Sil's title)

136
00:13:20,090 --> 00:13:24,490
Firstly, after we make it, we can make it our own, am I right?

137
00:13:31,110 --> 00:13:34,930
Your great fathers have requested and acquired

138
00:13:34,930 --> 00:13:37,980
a way for you to live.

139
00:13:37,980 --> 00:13:42,840
To avoid torture, you must instead pledge allegiance to become a Hwarang.

140
00:13:42,840 --> 00:13:46,340
All you have to do is sign this and go back home. Simple, right?

141
00:13:46,340 --> 00:13:50,870
Or, experience what the

142
00:13:50,870 --> 00:13:53,360
next step is for yourself.

143
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:55,090
Excuse me!

144
00:13:55,090 --> 00:14:00,080
So, if we write the oath, can we leave?

145
00:14:00,080 --> 00:14:01,050
That's right.

146
00:14:01,050 --> 00:14:05,080
Ah, you should have told us sooner. I was going to do that anyway.

147
00:14:05,080 --> 00:14:08,570
Here, untie me.

148
00:14:09,430 --> 00:14:13,220
If you are willing to sign, tell me right away.

149
00:14:13,820 --> 00:14:15,510
Untie me too!

150
00:14:15,510 --> 00:14:16,930
Me too!

151
00:14:16,930 --> 00:14:20,250
Untie me as well!

152
00:14:20,250 --> 00:14:22,800
Untie me too!

153
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:31,000
There is no way you aren't signing the oath just out of fear, right?

154
00:14:38,750 --> 00:14:42,020
Why? You don't want to write the oath?

155
00:14:42,020 --> 00:14:43,770
I want to do it.

156
00:14:44,900 --> 00:14:46,920
It looks like it will be fun.

157
00:14:46,920 --> 00:14:48,520
Then ask them to untie you quickly.

158
00:14:48,520 --> 00:14:50,730
But I'm not going to.

159
00:14:50,730 --> 00:14:54,200
- Why?
- Because I...

160
00:14:55,740 --> 00:14:58,340
I am the grandson of Seok Hyun Jae.

161
00:14:59,610 --> 00:15:01,040
Untie him too!

162
00:15:01,040 --> 00:15:03,330
Hyung, what are you doing?

163
00:15:04,130 --> 00:15:08,190
I'm half, so even if I write the oath, I can't become a Hwarang.

164
00:15:08,190 --> 00:15:14,310
But you're telling me that you're not going to be a Hwarang even if you want to?

165
00:15:14,310 --> 00:15:17,520
- Hyung.
- You're the Seok family's last True Bone.

166
00:15:17,520 --> 00:15:22,160
And Grandfather wouldn't want you to die here.

167
00:15:22,160 --> 00:15:24,510
♬ I will find the star.♬

168
00:15:24,510 --> 00:15:26,310
♬ Until I reach the dream♬

169
00:15:26,310 --> 00:15:29,840
Untie me too!
♬ suspended high in the sky♬

170
00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:32,330
♬ Even if darkness surrounds me ♬

171
00:15:32,330 --> 00:15:35,040
♬ You are the only one ♬

172
00:15:35,040 --> 00:15:37,490
♬ I will never throw away.♬

173
00:15:37,490 --> 00:15:43,400
♫ You'll always be mine ♫

174
00:15:52,300 --> 00:15:54,000
- What do you mean, you can't?
- To me...

175
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:59,000
You gave me full authority over the Hwarang.

176
00:15:59,800 --> 00:16:05,800
I did it so everything worked out the way we wanted.

177
00:16:05,800 --> 00:16:09,620
The arrogant officials who didn't show up during the ceremonial walk

178
00:16:09,620 --> 00:16:13,190
had to lower their tails like this.

179
00:16:13,190 --> 00:16:15,230
I knew you would do it.

180
00:16:15,230 --> 00:16:17,240
But, how come

181
00:16:17,240 --> 00:16:21,640
you are now asking me to accept any new Hwarang uncondtionally without quibbling, ?

182
00:16:21,700 --> 00:16:28,600
Exactly what kind of noblemen do you have in mind?

183
00:16:29,330 --> 00:16:34,020
Whoever I say, will you be able to accept them?

184
00:16:36,820 --> 00:16:40,900
How about this. Bring the one that you want.

185
00:16:40,900 --> 00:16:43,440
A Hwarang who doesn't question any condition.

186
00:16:43,440 --> 00:16:48,190
Then I will also not question it and just accept it as it is.

187
00:16:48,950 --> 00:16:51,290
What do you think?

188
00:17:01,330 --> 00:17:03,060
Come on!

189
00:17:08,530 --> 00:17:12,460
Please show courtesy as you receive the queen dowager's command.

190
00:17:17,790 --> 00:17:20,390
Ahn Ji Gong's son, Seon Woo,

191
00:17:20,390 --> 00:17:23,320
will be recruited as a Hwarang according to the queen dowager's orders.

192
00:17:23,320 --> 00:17:26,490
After ten days, come to Jowonjeon in Weolseong palace at noon

193
00:17:26,490 --> 00:17:29,890
to attend the Hwarang ceremony.

194
00:17:37,830 --> 00:17:39,720
Now...

195
00:17:40,960 --> 00:17:44,350
- will he be released?
- Wait.

196
00:17:44,350 --> 00:17:45,900
Let's go.

197
00:17:54,020 --> 00:17:55,800
Hwarang?

198
00:17:56,690 --> 00:18:01,080
You're becoming a Hwarang. What are they talking about?

199
00:18:01,080 --> 00:18:03,780
I don't want to.

200
00:18:06,190 --> 00:18:11,330
I have no desire to become a Hwarang under Queen Dowager Ji Soo even if I die.

201
00:18:21,120 --> 00:18:25,670
If you act like this is front of Yeong Sil, I will not let you go easily.

202
00:18:27,430 --> 00:18:31,040
Do you still think I'm a fearful, small child?

203
00:18:31,960 --> 00:18:35,170
Hit me as much as you want.

204
00:18:41,710 --> 00:18:44,980
You don't want to become a Hwarang?

205
00:18:46,030 --> 00:18:48,560
You shouldn't have made trouble.

206
00:18:48,560 --> 00:18:52,570
I sincerely apologize. He is very stubborn.

207
00:19:14,460 --> 00:19:16,820
Are you miserable?

208
00:19:21,650 --> 00:19:24,080
That is how power is.

209
00:19:24,080 --> 00:19:27,000
If you cannot wield power, you can't do anything except submit.

210
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:30,390
What can you do? You have to choose.

211
00:19:30,390 --> 00:19:33,160
Will you wield it?

212
00:19:34,000 --> 00:19:36,600
Don't think this is miserable?

213
00:19:36,600 --> 00:19:40,160
The world is different from what you imagine.

214
00:19:41,420 --> 00:19:44,120
It's much dirtier.

215
00:19:52,100 --> 00:19:54,470
Become a Hwarang!

216
00:19:54,470 --> 00:19:57,240
Go and get power!

217
00:20:00,230 --> 00:20:04,100
I'm going to make your son a Hwarang.

218
00:20:04,100 --> 00:20:09,050
I'm going to raise your son as a dog for my son.

219
00:20:09,050 --> 00:20:13,440
If it's Hwarang, I heard it will be the future of Silla.

220
00:20:14,690 --> 00:20:19,170
Did you really think Hwarang will be responsible for Silla?

221
00:20:19,170 --> 00:20:22,200
Did you think it was a place to raise talent?

222
00:20:23,230 --> 00:20:25,980
The children of the wolves who are hunting for the king's life

223
00:20:25,980 --> 00:20:28,120
will be locked and tamed as Hwarang.

224
00:20:28,120 --> 00:20:30,880
They will be faithful dogs, who for my son's sake,

225
00:20:30,880 --> 00:20:34,390
will give their lives or hunting dogs that lose their lives.

226
00:20:34,390 --> 00:20:38,570
What made you this way, Queen Dowager?

227
00:20:38,570 --> 00:20:41,050
Your son's life

228
00:20:41,880 --> 00:20:44,540
is in my hands.

229
00:20:46,000 --> 00:20:48,940
Don't forget that for a moment.

230
00:21:10,330 --> 00:21:12,540
Father...

231
00:21:17,440 --> 00:21:19,720
It's not a big deal.

232
00:21:20,830 --> 00:21:23,930
Look your father is alright.

233
00:21:29,940 --> 00:21:31,980
You were worried, weren't you?

234
00:21:35,400 --> 00:21:37,680
Where is your brother?

235
00:21:37,680 --> 00:21:39,910
You should leave.

236
00:21:39,910 --> 00:21:42,740
The queen dowager is not sparing your life.

237
00:21:42,740 --> 00:21:45,360
Hwarang is full of shackles to kill you.

238
00:21:45,360 --> 00:21:47,880
So, run away right now.

239
00:21:48,610 --> 00:21:50,700
I can't leave like this.

240
00:21:53,120 --> 00:21:55,450
No.

241
00:21:55,450 --> 00:22:00,380
Going against the queen dowager is just as reckless as dousing yourself in oil and leaping into a fire.

242
00:22:00,380 --> 00:22:02,590
I know that.

243
00:22:08,450 --> 00:22:10,380
I...

244
00:22:11,160 --> 00:22:13,730
If I can protect you, I am fine.

245
00:22:17,090 --> 00:22:20,890
I will do it, Hwarang.

246
00:22:20,890 --> 00:22:23,430
It's not somewhere where you'd want to stay.

247
00:22:23,430 --> 00:22:26,860
It will be worse than anything you are thinking.

248
00:22:29,110 --> 00:22:30,980
I will endure it!

249
00:22:30,980 --> 00:22:34,270
I will go and see whatever there is to the end of this wretched capital.

250
00:22:34,270 --> 00:22:37,930
I will go see. I will go and break everything.

251
00:22:37,930 --> 00:22:40,120
So...

252
00:22:40,120 --> 00:22:43,000
I will join Hwarang.

253
00:22:50,510 --> 00:22:52,670
My horse is outside.

254
00:22:52,670 --> 00:22:55,090
Is Wi Hwa Gong not here yet?

255
00:22:56,520 --> 00:22:59,190
What are you doing and not tying it?

256
00:22:59,190 --> 00:23:03,480
