How handsome!

516
00:46:01,020 --> 00:46:02,670
Huh?

517
00:46:13,730 --> 00:46:16,570
Goal!

518
00:46:16,570 --> 00:46:20,330
You are all dead!

519
00:46:20,330 --> 00:46:21,800
2 points

520
00:46:21,800 --> 00:46:23,730
Is he totally dumb?

521
00:46:23,730 --> 00:46:26,020
Not this side, this one! This side!

522
00:46:26,020 --> 00:46:29,630
You scored in our goal!

523
00:46:30,620 --> 00:46:31,970
It was that side?

524
00:46:31,970 --> 00:46:33,760
Sheesh.

525
00:46:58,360 --> 00:46:59,630
1 point

526
00:47:00,870 --> 00:47:02,890
Hooray!

527
00:47:50,700 --> 00:47:52,900
2 points

528
00:48:00,580 --> 00:48:04,720
See? What did I tell you?! He's different!

529
00:48:10,700 --> 00:48:12,920
What are you doing?

530
00:48:14,700 --> 00:48:17,190
He's a total monster.

531
00:48:17,890 --> 00:48:20,680
We can't ever lose this one.

532
00:48:24,500 --> 00:48:26,800
Let's go.

533
00:48:39,520 --> 00:48:41,450
Hey, hey!

534
00:48:41,450 --> 00:48:43,500
You surprised me.

535
00:48:44,490 --> 00:48:46,070
"Hey"?

536
00:48:46,070 --> 00:48:49,130
Have you ever even held a ball before?

537
00:48:49,130 --> 00:48:52,190
You should have let me know if you like these things.

538
00:48:52,190 --> 00:48:54,470
It's not like that.

539
00:48:54,470 --> 00:48:55,920
I did make an assumption,

540
00:48:55,920 --> 00:49:01,910
but you're worse than I thought, so I was the surprised one as you said.

541
00:49:01,910 --> 00:49:04,260
Shut your mouth.

542
00:49:05,590 --> 00:49:09,290
What? Do you have a plan?

543
00:49:17,820 --> 00:49:21,420
Don't smile. You annoy me.

544
00:49:54,650 --> 00:49:55,540
What the—

545
00:49:55,540 --> 00:49:56,660
What? What's with you?

546
00:49:56,660 --> 00:49:58,900
What are you doing? You're on the same team!

547
00:50:01,650 --> 00:50:04,770
You bastard!

548
00:50:04,770 --> 00:50:08,280
♬ When the path on which I fearlessly♬

549
00:50:08,300 --> 00:50:13,730
♬ went out and searched for the small dream♬

550
00:50:13,730 --> 00:50:18,360
♬ which was concealed in the flickering starlight♬

551
00:50:18,400 --> 00:50:23,800
♬ was more than I could bear♬

552
00:50:23,900 --> 00:50:29,400
♫  You were there. Like a dream  ♫

553
00:50:29,400 --> 00:50:34,490
♫  then another world which I came to know ♬

554
00:50:34,490 --> 00:50:39,820
♬ and even a shard of my crushed heart ♬

555
00:50:39,820 --> 00:50:42,770
♬ became a light in your breath.♬

556
00:50:42,770 --> 00:50:44,210
Good job!

557
00:50:44,300 --> 00:50:48,900
Yes! Yes! That's right!

558
00:50:48,920 --> 00:50:53,060
♫  All I need is only you  ♫

559
00:50:53,060 --> 00:50:55,460
2 Points
♬ I will find the star.♬

560
00:50:55,500 --> 00:51:00,100
3 Points
♬ Until I reach the dream suspended high in the sky ♬

561
00:51:00,120 --> 00:51:03,290
♫  Even if darkness surrounds me  ♫

562
00:51:03,300 --> 00:51:06,320
♬ You are the only one ♬

563
00:51:06,320 --> 00:51:09,700
♬ I will never throw away.♬

564
00:51:09,760 --> 00:51:10,900
Ah, okay.

565
00:51:10,900 --> 00:51:16,900
♬ You will get a small wish. Soon♬

566
00:51:17,000 --> 00:51:22,300
♫  You will become a flower  ♫
What was that?

567
00:51:23,190 --> 00:51:27,160
♫  All I need is only you  ♫

568
00:51:27,160 --> 00:51:29,730
♫  I will find the star ♫

569
00:51:29,800 --> 00:51:33,800
♬ Until I reach the dream suspended high in the sky ♬

570
00:51:33,850 --> 00:51:37,500
♫  Even if darkness surrounds me  ♫

571
00:51:42,710 --> 00:51:49,060
You fall so much, but surprisingly you have more physical strength than I expected.

572
00:51:49,060 --> 00:51:51,450
With the horse, too.

573
00:51:52,820 --> 00:51:56,530
I am thankful for earlier, for saving me.

574
00:52:08,240 --> 00:52:12,160
But you're not close friends with that young nobleman earlier, are you?

575
00:52:12,160 --> 00:52:14,830
Ah, seriously. He didn't seem like a good person.

576
00:52:14,830 --> 00:52:20,640
No, at the Okta Shop. Oh not that, we just slept—

577
00:52:22,400 --> 00:52:26,010
You're crazy. Keep your mouth shut.

578
00:52:30,300 --> 00:52:32,310
Ride my back.

579
00:52:33,860 --> 00:52:36,120
You're hurt.

580
00:52:36,120 --> 00:52:38,490
I'm alright though.

581
00:52:39,270 --> 00:52:41,320
Then do you want me to carry you?

582
00:52:47,160 --> 00:52:54,470
♬ Don't look at me with sad eyes ♬

583
00:52:54,470 --> 00:53:01,790
♬ Your aching heart displays everything♬

584
00:53:01,790 --> 00:53:05,350
Why, out of all men, does it have to be him?
♬ If you keep doing that ♬

585
00:53:05,350 --> 00:53:09,460
♫  You will just leave me  ♫

586
00:53:09,500 --> 00:53:17,000
♬ When you only offer me tears, what can I do?♬

587
00:53:18,950 --> 00:53:22,360
Was your personality always rough?

588
00:53:22,360 --> 00:53:25,760
You can't act that way in the capital.

589
00:53:25,760 --> 00:53:30,000
Everything is built upon connections. It's true!

590
00:53:30,000 --> 00:53:34,770
♫ I'm afraid I will be left yearning. ♫

591
00:53:34,770 --> 00:53:44,030
♫  So I can't let you go ♫

592
00:53:47,280 --> 00:53:56,200
♬ Although you and I became tears for each other♬

593
00:53:56,200 --> 00:54:03,800
♫  After time passed on a bright day  ♫

594
00:54:03,820 --> 00:54:06,250
♬ when we just held each other... ♬

595
00:54:15,280 --> 00:54:17,370
Kim Seon Woo

596
00:54:17,370 --> 00:54:20,460
I told you to hurry up!

597
00:54:22,220 --> 00:54:23,960
We'll be late at this rate.

598
00:54:23,960 --> 00:54:27,770
No way. I came out early. How can I be late?

599
00:54:33,750 --> 00:54:35,800
Let's see.

600
00:54:39,970 --> 00:54:41,820
Wait a moment.

601
00:55:09,560 --> 00:55:12,160
Aigo. What can we do?

602
00:55:12,160 --> 00:55:15,080
I like this too.

603
00:55:15,770 --> 00:55:20,130
Th-Then take it.

604
00:55:20,130 --> 00:55:22,520
Are you Ahn Ji Gong's daughter?

605
00:55:25,130 --> 00:55:27,410
How do you know me?

606
00:55:31,200 --> 00:55:33,910
Pull like this...

607
00:56:12,060 --> 00:56:13,900
Hwarang?

608
00:56:21,480 --> 00:56:23,090
What is this?

609
00:56:24,420 --> 00:56:28,130
Is he going to the ceremony right now, wearing that bracelet like that?

610
00:57:01,800 --> 00:57:05,040
How can a Cheonin wear silk like this?

611
00:57:05,040 --> 00:57:08,080
Looks like you've settled well in the capital.

612
00:57:08,080 --> 00:57:11,390
Settle the issue with me. Let her go.

613
00:57:11,390 --> 00:57:16,860
Wow, it's the first time I've seen Dog-Bird Gong being this scared.

614
00:57:16,860 --> 00:57:20,560
I think it's because of that girl.

615
00:57:27,090 --> 00:57:29,500
I said let her go.

616
00:57:29,500 --> 00:57:31,620
Stay there.

617
00:57:33,040 --> 00:57:35,820
He was loitering around outside.

618
00:57:44,270 --> 00:57:48,990
That girl's life is on the line based on what you do.

619
00:57:48,990 --> 00:57:52,320
If you touch one strand of her hair,

620
00:57:52,320 --> 00:57:54,320
you're dead.

621
00:57:56,000 --> 00:57:59,690
Let's see. Before I die,

622
00:57:59,690 --> 00:58:02,500
aren't you going to die first?

623
00:58:02,500 --> 00:58:04,890
No, right now!

624
00:58:10,670 --> 00:58:15,050
If you want to kill me, kill me. But if she get's hurt before that,

625
00:58:15,050 --> 00:58:16,990
you'll die in my hands.

626
00:58:24,860 --> 00:58:30,090
♫  A slight sprinkle is falling, black tears cover me ♫

627
00:58:30,090 --> 00:58:35,300
♫  In my two red eyes, I boxed you up ♫
